collect">藏品</a><ul class="secmenu"><li><a aria-current="page" class="active" target="_self" href="#/Collection/collect">文物赏析</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Collection/culcreate">文化创意</a></li></ul></li><li class=""><a target="_self" href="#/Education/baseres">教育</a><ul class="secmenu"><li><a target="_self" href="#/Education/baseres">基地资源</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Education/volunteer">志愿者之家</a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="http://dj.shaoqiguli.com">党教展馆</a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="/young.html">青少年教育</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Education/societyeducation">社会教育</a></li></ul></li><li class=""><a target="_self" href="#/Research/academic">学术</a><ul class="secmenu"><li><a target="_self" href="#/Research/academic">学术委员会</a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="http://202.197.127.133/lsq/default.asp">学术数据库</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Research/journals">数字馆刊</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Research/resact">学术活动</a></li></ul></li><li class=""><a target="_self" href="#/Scenicspot/viewscan">景区</a><ul class="secmenu"><li><a target="_self" href="#/Scenicspot/viewscan">景点速览</a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="https://baike.baidu.com/museum/liushaoqi">数字景区</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Scenicspot/videoapp">视频赏析</a></li></ul></li><li class=""><a target="_self" href="#/Column/partywork">专栏</a><ul class="secmenu"><li><a target="_self" href="#/Column/partywork">党务专栏</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Column/civcreate">文明创建</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Column/shiningexample?listType=img">五个光辉榜样</a></li></ul></li><li class=""><a target="_self" href="#/Interaction/newmedia">服务</a><ul class="secmenu"><li><a target="_self" href="#/Interaction/newmedia">新媒体服务</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Interaction/guide">参观指南</a></li><li><a target="_self" href="#/Interaction/messageboard">留言板</a></li></ul></li></ul><div class="secright"><ul class="ewmbox"><li><p>官方微信</p><img src="assets/ewm-weixin.29093721.jpg" alt="官方微信"></l